mlflex.dataprocessors
Class AbstractMetadataProcessor

java.lang.Object
  mlflex.dataprocessors.AbstractMetadataProcessor
Direct Known Subclasses:
ChromosomeBandMetadataProcessor, GenePositionMetadataProcessor, TcgaCghMetadataProcessor, TcgaMethylationMetadataProcessor, TcgaMrnaMetadataProcessor
public abstract class AbstractMetadataProcessor
extends java.lang.Object

This abstract class coordinates all tasks for processing, storing, and describing metadata. Custom classes can inherit from this class in order to process new metadata.

Author:
Stephen Piccolo
